OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy periods during the
OL,6,Fmorning with showers developing. The
OL,7,Fbest of the sunshine will likely be in
OL,8,Fthe evening as the cloud break and
OL,9,Fshowers dissipate.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FAny remaining showers should
OL,12,Fquickly fade to leave a dry and
OL,13,Fsettled night with prolonged clear
OL,14,Fspells and light winds.
OL,15,
OL,16,CMonday:FA clear start to the morning
OL,17,Fbut quickly clouding over with rain to
OL,18,Ffollow. Remaining rather grey and wet
OL,19,Fduring the afternoon with heavy
OL,20,Foutbreaks of rain possible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
