OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FThe
OL,6,Funsettled theme continues with bands
OL,7,Fof rain moving and showery outbreaks
OL,8,Fat times. The wind will strengthen
OL,9,Fcompared to previous days with
OL,10,Ftemperatures returning to around
OL,11,Fnormal.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
